<item>
            <title>[OAK-1168] Invalid JCR paths not caught</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-1168</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;NamePathMapper.getOakPath&lt;/tt&gt; should return &lt;tt&gt;null&lt;/tt&gt; when called with an invalid JCR path like &lt;tt&gt;foo:bar]baz&lt;/tt&gt;, but it doesn&apos;t. &lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12678763">OAK-1168</key>
            <summary>Invalid JCR paths not caught</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
